{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256730/extras/GIF_Shoot_Zombie_2_Cropped.gif?t=1735314630\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256730/extras/M37.gif?t=1735314630\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256730/extras/MP5Shoot_Optimized_Cropped.gif?t=1735314630\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256730/extras/Type99.gif?t=1735314630\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No Life is a brutal survival roguelite where you\u2019ll face endless hordes of relentless zombies in a battle for survival. Choose from a varied roster of survivors, each equipped with unique abilities and playstyles, allowing you to customize your approach to every encounter. You can also acquire a loyal dog companion by your side, adding an extra layer of support in combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256730/extras/GIF_Horde-optimized.gif?t=1735314630\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prepare for an increasingly intense fight against the undead. Scavenge for powerful weapons and items scattered throughout procedurally generated environments. Adapt your strategy as you encounter different types of zombies, each presenting its own challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade your character's skills and unlock new abilities as you progress, creating devastating combinations that can turn the tide of battle. With each wave, the hordes grow stronger, pushing you to improve your tactics and explore new synergies among your survivors, weapons, and your canine companion.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256730/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735314630","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256730/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1735314630","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256730/3f4afc1f889f32815da018c4a4db969e1dcd8091/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735314630","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256730/3f4afc1f889f32815da018c4a4db969e1dcd8091/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735314630","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"Blood and gore from pixel zombies. No real pixel characters were harmed during the development of this game. "},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256730/extras/GIF_Shoot_Zombie_2_Cropped.gif?t=1735314630\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256730/extras/M37.gif?t=1735314630\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256730/extras/MP5Shoot_Optimized_Cropped.gif?t=1735314630\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256730/extras/Type99.gif?t=1735314630\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No Life is a brutal survival roguelite where you\u2019ll face endless hordes of relentless zombies in a battle for survival. Choose from a varied roster of survivors, each equipped with unique abilities and playstyles, allowing you to customize your approach to every encounter. You can also acquire a loyal dog companion by your side, adding an extra layer of support in combat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256730/extras/GIF_Horde-optimized.gif?t=1735314630\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prepare for an increasingly intense fight against the undead. Scavenge for powerful weapons and items scattered throughout procedurally generated environments. Adapt your strategy as you encounter different types of zombies, each presenting its own challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade your character's skills and unlock new abilities as you progress, creating devastating combinations that can turn the tide of battle. With each wave, the hordes grow stronger, pushing you to improve your tactics and explore new synergies among your survivors, weapons, and your canine companion.</p>","developers":["VaragtP"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1256730/header.jpg?t=1735314630","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257068045,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257068045/movie480.mp4?t=1729866552","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257068045/movie_max.mp4?t=1729866552"},"name":"No Life Teaser Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257068045/ce89e9933c5f2c4480b2ed55d9f4449674525bc6/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1729866552","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257068045/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1729866552","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257068045/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1729866552"}}],"name":"No Life","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements"